{"tid":2101680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我俾上司針對, 可以點算","createTime":"2020-07-10T03:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:39:10.000Z","uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"adaf4530b869db88712895cf6881ae44aa356304","tid":2101680,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\">其實, 全公司都知佢刻意針對我, 不過個個都怕左我直屬上司, 原因係佢好似精神有少少問題 - 時時神不守社, 冇啦啦發脾氣, 大老細都唔敢亂黎, 怕左佢 ...<br />\n<br />\n佢針對我o既方法:<br />\n1. 週圍同人講話我幫唔到手.<br />\n2. 成日都搵我做野, 通常俾三日時間我, 不過係星期五放工後先通知我, 同星期一九點前要完成. (註: 我五天工作)<br />\n3. 當面問佢問題, 佢就話email 會講清楚, 之後佢會send email 俾我. 但email就會話 &quot;as discussed clearly already, ...&quot; (即係冇答)<br />\n4. 係寫字樓用手機/相機, 拍低我工作情況 (我有少少提心吊膽, 好似成日俾人跟蹤咁)<br />\n5. 要我著短過膝既裙<br />\n大老細唔鍾意麻煩, 對佢黎講, 最緊要小事化冇. hr 都唔理.</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"589eec9beeeddb783b6557a27d629e1c464a21b6","tid":2101680,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"決定block 太煩"},{"pid":"7ec1a98619daed8d2b3e77c76e098cf146dfb6f2","tid":2101680,"uid":63822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">日日話手足係condom<br />\n要接管晒手足的女人</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#56875 - 人善被人J</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (5)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fyDErT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fyDErT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxtKzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxtKzT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/fxnxcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/fxnxcT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><